intro: A classic escape game set in an art museum hosting an exhibition of past works!
description:
■Game System
This is an escape game (puzzle-solving adventure game).
※ Progress through the game by selecting items on the screen with the cursor and solving various puzzles.

■Story
I heard a special event featuring my favorite “Cat Series” escape game was happening at the nearby museum, so I came to check it out.

Cat
“Welcome to the event, meow! Do you like escape games, meow?”

It seems you get a souvenir if you escape successfully.

Let's jump right in and give it a try!
